LINE.Text: Demand for additional tourism workers is estimated
to grow by 123,000 including 60,000 skilled by 2020
a) 'Transport includes air, water, rail and other transport b) Travel services' includes travel agency and tour operator
services c) 'Clubs and pubs' also includes taverns and bars.
Sources Tourism Research Australia State Tourism Satellite Account 2013-14; Australian Bureau of Statistics, National
